summary:
Currently, I am in the third year of my Bachelor of Economics at Tilburg University and so far this degree has provided me with a great foundation of knowledge and skills in different areas of Economics such as Finance, Accounting, Data analysis, Statistics, Econometrics and others.

I am an ambitious person who easily adapts to a dynamic environment. I believe I have a resourceful approach to problem-solving and I consider obstacles as learning experiences. I'm an open-minded and creative person with high energy.
